&lt;blockquote class=&#34;twitter-tweet&#34;&gt;&lt;p lang=&#34;en&#34; dir=&#34;ltr&#34;&gt;1/ New paper out! &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/Brain1878?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;@Brain1878&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://t.co/l3VIfg4s9F&#34;&gt;https://t.co/l3VIfg4s9F&lt;/a&gt; Robust &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/hashtag/MachineLearning?src=hash&amp;amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;#MachineLearning&lt;/a&gt; of diagnosis from &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/hashtag/EEG?src=hash&amp;amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;#EEG&lt;/a&gt; in disorders of &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/hashtag/consciousness?src=hash&amp;amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;#consciousness&lt;/a&gt; powered by &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/CEAParisSaclay?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;@CEAParisSaclay&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/cdf1530?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;@cdf1530&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/Coma_Science?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;@Coma_Science&lt;/a&gt; @dc_uba &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/ERC_Research?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;@ERC_Research&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/Inria_Saclay?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;@Inria_Saclay&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/Inserm?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;@Inserm&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/mne_news?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;@mne_news&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/NeuroSpin_91?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;@NeuroSpin_91&lt;/a&gt; @icm_institute &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/scikit_learn?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;@scikit_learn&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://t.co/JsDMUYWw6C&#34;&gt;pic.twitter.com/JsDMUYWw6C&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&amp;mdash; Denis A. Engemann (@dngman) &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/dngman/status/1047774447422394368?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;October 4, 2018&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
